                                <h4>Dimitar Ivanov</h4>
                                <p>Core Developer, æternity Crypto Foundation</p>
                                <div class="content-bio">
                                    <p>Dimitar is a software engineer from Bulgaria. He has been part of the AE core team for the past 5 years. Initially a crypto sceptic, Dimitar turned into a crypto enthusiast.</p>
                                    <p>All questions regarding technology are welcome but please no questions "Should I buy X?"</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
